title: Do not require <<project>>
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Instead of using the ``<<project>>`` macro within tiddlers, detect projects with the <<tag Project>> tag, and todos with the  <<tag todo>> tag.

Todo tiddlers with sub tasks can be rendered as projects using a filter to find if it has todos. Otherwise, add a button to add a first subtask.